  "texts": [
    "The early diagnosis of leaf diseases is essential for maintaining the health and productivity of crops.",
    "The implementation of efficient disease control techniques, the reduction of crop losses, and the maintenance of sustainable agricultural practices all depend on the prompt and correct detection of plant diseases.",
    "Pre-trained models and advances in deep learning have recently demonstrated promising outcomes in several computer vision tasks, including the identification of leaf disease.",
    "This research paper provides a thorough examination of custom convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for efficient leaf disease detection.",
    "The purpose of this research is to compare the performance of pre-trained models to determine the optimal architecture for accurate and fast disease classification."
